OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,FCardiff could become the first local
OL,7,Fauthority in Wales to introduce a
OL,8,Ftourism tax on paid overnight stays.
OL,10,FThe fee would be #1.30 per person per
OL,11,Fnight for most accommodation types,
OL,12,Fand 75 per person per night for
OL,13,Fcampsites and shared rooms like
OL,14,Fhostels.
