OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,FCertain groups would be exempt,
OL,7,Fincluding children under 18 staying in
OL,8,Fcampsites or shared rooms, people
OL,9,Fstaying more than 31 consecutive
OL,10,Fnights in one booking, and those
OL,11,Fplaced in emergency or temporary
OL,12,Fhousing arranged by the council.
OL,14,FWelsh legislation allows councils to
OL,15,Fbring in a Visitor Levy for overnight
OL,16,Fvisitors from April 2027.
