OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,FCardiff Council is now preparing to,
OL,7,Fsubject to cabinet approval, launch a
OL,8,F12-week consultation from December 1
OL,9,Fabout introducing the fee, which would
OL,10,Fapply to paid overnight stays of 31
OL,11,Fnights or less in hotels, hostels,
OL,12,Fguesthouses, Airbnbs, campsites and
OL,13,Ftemporary event accommodation.
OL,15,FMoney raised - which the council
OL,16,Festimates to be #3.5million per year,
OL,17,Fwould be paid to the Welsh Revenue
OL,18,FAuthority, who would pay the levy to
OL,19,Flocal authorities.
