OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,FA council statement said: "The money
OL,7,Fraised would be used to support
OL,8,FCardiff's visitor economy, through
OL,9,Fdestination management and
OL,10,Fimprovement, which would include
OL,11,Fimproving infrastructure, promoting
OL,12,Fevents, supporting tourism businesses,
OL,13,Fand enhancing the city's appeal to
OL,14,Fvisitors."
OL,16,FThe results of the consultation are
OL,17,Fset to be presented to Cardiff's full
OL,18,Fcouncil and cabinet, in March 2026 for
OL,19,Fapproval.
