OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,FCouncillor Russell Goodway, cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for investment and development,
OL,8,Fsaid the proposed levy aims to enhance
OL,9,FCardiff's appeal to visitors.
OL,11,FHe said: "The proposed Visitor Levy in
OL,12,FCardiff would be used to improve the
OL,13,Fvisitor experience for everyone coming
OL,14,Fto Cardiff, by funding marketing
OL,15,Fcampaigns, or by supporting a broader
OL,16,Frange of events in the city. Not only
OL,17,Fdo we want people to enjoy their
OL,18,Fexperience coming to Cardiff, but we
OL,19,Falso want people to stay longer, so we
OL,20,Fneed to increase our offer though
OL,21,Finvestment.
