OL,3,CCardiff could become first place in
OL,4,CWales to introduce tourism tax
OL,6,F"The proposed charge, set out in
OL,7,Flegislation, is significantly lower
OL,8,Fthan the typical charge across Europe.
OL,10,F"If the proposed Visitor Levy is
OL,11,Fagreed by Cabinet and Full Council, a
OL,12,FVisitor Levy Partnership Forum will be
OL,13,Fset up to advise on how the funds are
OL,14,Fused and will help shape Cardiff's
OL,15,FTourism Strategy. Final decisions on
OL,16,Fthe spending of the money raised will
OL,17,Fremain with elected officials."
